    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEEPLANDERS 是一款极简风格的建造与解谜游戏，围绕着在地下深处建立社群展开。</strong><br><strong>这是一种轻松的体验，你可以建造温馨的地下城市，同时为每位 Deeplander 找到和谐生活的完美位置。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192550/extras/1d51de88213e1e9ef8e67e435fb6c068.poster.avif?t=1771852656\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192550/extras/1d51de88213e1e9ef8e67e435fb6c068.webm?t=1771852656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192550/extras/1d51de88213e1e9ef8e67e435fb6c068.mp4?t=1771852656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被迫生活在地下，这些可爱的角色在黑暗中徘徊迷失。随着你的建设，他们会逐渐到来，寻找一个可以安身立命的地方。并非所有人都渴望相同的生活，让每位 Deeplander 找到自己的位置，成为一个温和而引人入胜的逻辑挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192550/extras/8891872a679f115349dd131bb8282dfe.poster.avif?t=1771852656\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192550/extras/8891872a679f115349dd131bb8282dfe.webm?t=1771852656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192550/extras/8891872a679f115349dd131bb8282dfe.mp4?t=1771852656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当一座城市完成后，选择权在你手中。你可以一边装饰环境，一边观察 Deeplanders 的日常生活，或是继续深入未知的深处。每一次下探都会书写他们故事的新篇章，加入新的角色、场景与建造方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个深度都可以通过多种方式完成，鼓励你反复游玩并创造不同的城市。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192550/extras/14c38881f53eb817327f8da88c3e9ca4.poster.avif?t=1771852656\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192550/extras/14c38881f53eb817327f8da88c3e9ca4.webm?t=1771852656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192550/extras/14c38881f53eb817327f8da88c3e9ca4.mp4?t=1771852656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>请注意，DEEPLANDERS 是一款用心制作但规模不大的游戏。它邀请你建造、尝试并塑造小型地下城市...因为即使在最深处，也可以成为美丽的地方。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在 DEEPLANDERS 中，你可以：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照自己的节奏建造并装饰地下城市。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决小型的布局与组织类谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受轻松而富有沉思感的游戏体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重复游玩同一深度，尝试不同的解决方案。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DEEPLANDERS 不包含：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采矿或复杂的资源管理。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗、失败状态或排行榜。</p></li></ul>",
